Robert Gottschall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Gottschall 0 Robert Gottschall, also known as Robert Shaw (15 September 1915 – 3 January 2005), was an American actor. A United States Army lieutenant colonel in World War II and the Korean War, he was buried at the Fort Sam Houston National Cemetery in San Antonio, Texas.
